## Sprint 0

### Session 006

Approved the Dog concept.

Introduced observation-based understanding instead of fixed personality labels.

Confirmed that Capabilities and Challenges are always evaluated in Context.

### Session 007

Approved the Relationship concept.

Introduced the six relationship dimensions.

Introduced the concept of a Relationship Superpower.

Confirmed that relationships are never compared or ranked.

## Sprint 0

### Session 008

Approved the Context model.

Introduced Context Factors.

Confirmed that behaviours are always evaluated within Context.

Completed a design review of Family, Context, Dog and Relationship.

### Session 009

Approved the Goal concept.

Introduced Family Goals and Personal Goals.

Confirmed that every Goal requires a Why.

Established that Missions are always linked to Goals.

### Session 010

Approved the Mission concept.

Introduced Mission Templates.

Introduced four Mission types.

Established that every Mission must contribute to learning, relationships, progress or meaningful memories.

### Session 011

Approved the Insight concept.

Introduced four Insight types.

Confirmed that Insights are interpretations rather than facts.

Established that Insights require sufficient evidence before being shown.